        <span id="“They_taught_us_very_young_how_to_serve_and_what_to_look_for_in">
        <span id="textspandss23">“Well, all I know is that I love Doug and Skip dearly. They have been wonderful examples to their family. They are there to help family and neighbors when in need. They are always interested in you and care about you and your well being.”</span><span id="textspandss24"><br /></span><span id="textspandss25">&#x7e; Linda Niccum, Sister of Doug</span>
